      "Ensures business continuity",
      "Maximizes business value",
      "Provides for owner's retirement",
      "Minimizes taxes and legal complications",
      "Protects employees and stakeholders"
    ],
    "key_decisions": [
      "Who will take over the business?",
      "When will the transition occur?",
      "How will ownership transfer?",
      "How will the owner be compensated?",
      "What is the tax-optimal structure?"
    ]
  },
